        <abstract> 
<p>Sends more <hi rend="italic">Trifolium resupinatum</hi>.</p> 
            <p>In France as in England there is indignation at the insults Decaisne suffered in the last years of his life.</p>
            <p>Charles Martins has lost his Professorship at Montpellier.</p>
